Sentencas: A method based on X-ray reflectivity was used to study the densification behavior of 8 mol% yttria-stabilized zirconia for use in solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Rapid densification of sol-gel derived yttria-stabilized zirconia thin films

Sentencas: Sol-gel derived thin electrolyte films were prepared via spin coating.
Titulo: Rapid densification of sol-gel derived yttria-stabilized zirconia thin films

Sentencas: Subsequent microwave-assisted rapid thermal annealing at 650-1000 degrees C resulted in crack-free 70 nm thin films.
Titulo: Rapid densification of sol-gel derived yttria-stabilized zirconia thin films

Sentencas: A maximum density of approximately 95% was achieved within 5 min at 1000 degrees C. X-ray photoelectron spectroscopy depth analysis on the thin films showed that the shorter annealing times, as opposed to conventional heating, resulted in lower Si concentrations at the top surface and at the substrate interface.
Titulo: Rapid densification of sol-gel derived yttria-stabilized zirconia thin films
